## Changelog

### 1.4.0

* Adding integration for [FAIRsharing.org](https://fairsharing.org)
* Adding 5 integration questions according to [ds-km@da5a8fc](https://github.com/ds-wizard/ds-km/commit/da5a8fc95d0a67f9369ce0b7727615115fc3656d).

